@startuml docker_gce_session_start
' DockerGCEProvider 経由のセッション開始シーケンス
title Docker on GCE — セッション開始シーケンス\n(getOrCreateEndpoint → VM Ready 2段階確認 → cc-remote-agent HTTP実行)

participant Browser
participant "cc-tunnel API\n(handler.go)" as CloudRun
participant "DockerGCEProvider\n[ExecutionProvider]" as Provider
participant PostgreSQL as DB
participant "GCE API" as GCEAPI
participant "GCE VM\n(Packer Ubuntu+Docker)" as VM
participant "container-manager\n(VM 常駐 :9090)" as CM
participant "cc-remote-agent\nContainer" as Container

Browser -> CloudRun: POST /api/conversations\n(新規会話作成)
CloudRun -> DB: INSERT conversation
CloudRun --> Browser: 201 Created {id, status: "idle"}

Browser -> CloudRun: POST /api/conversations/{id}/messages\n{content: "Hello"}

CloudRun -> Provider: Execute(ctx, req, onEvent)\n[ExecutionProvider.Execute()]

Provider -> Provider: getOrCreateEndpoint(conversationID)\n[singleflight でコンカレント重複排除]

Provider -> DB: GetSessionEndpointByConversationID(conversationID)

alt エンドポイントあり (warm path)
  DB --> Provider: {vmInstanceID, port, status: "running"}
  Provider -> DB: GetVMInstance(vmInstanceID)
  DB --> Provider: {internalIP, ...}
  note over Provider: agentURL = http://{internalIP}:{port}

else エンドポイントなし (cold path)
  DB --> Provider: レコードなし

  Provider -> DB: GetAvailableVMInstance(maxContainers)

  alt 利用可能 VM あり (warm VM)
    DB --> Provider: {id, internalIP, activeContainers < max}

  else VM なし → 新規 VM 作成
    DB --> Provider: エラー(なし)
    Provider -> GCEAPI: CreateInstance(project, zone,\n  machineType, vmImage)
    note over GCEAPI,VM
      VM イメージ (Packer Ubuntu+Docker) に
      container-manager systemd unit を焼き込み済み:
      1. dockerd は Unix socket バインド (TCP 2375 なし)
      2. container-manager (:9090) が起動時に常駐
      3. cc-remote-agent は cc-tunnel の要求時に
         container-manager の RunAgent で逐次起動
    end note
    GCEAPI --> Provider: {name: "cc-tunnel-xxxx"}
    Provider -> DB: CreateVMInstance(gceInstanceName, zone, ip)

    note over Provider: waitForVMReady() — 2段階確認

    loop Stage 1: GCE RUNNING + internalIP 取得\n(タイムアウト: 3分, ポーリング: 5秒)
      Provider -> GCEAPI: GetInstance(project, zone, vmName)
      GCEAPI --> Provider: {status, networkIP}
      alt status="RUNNING" && networkIP != ""
        note over Provider: Stage 1 完了
        break
      end
    end

    Provider -> DB: UpdateVMInstanceIP(vmID, internalIP)

    loop Stage 2a: container-manager 疎通確認\n(ポーリング)
      Provider -> CM: GET /v1/agents (HTTP :9090)
      alt 応答あり (HTTP 200)
        note over Provider: container-manager Ready
        break
      end
    end

    Provider -> CM: RunAgent(image, hostPort)\n(pull + run を 1 step で)
    CM -> VM: dockerd に pull/run (Unix socket)
    VM --> Container: cc-remote-agent 起動

    loop Stage 2b: cc-remote-agent health check\n(タイムアウト: 1分, ポーリング: 5秒)
      Provider -> Container: GET /auth/status\n(remoteclient.GetAuthStatus)
      alt 応答あり (HTTP 200)
        note over Provider: Stage 2 完了 → VM/Agent Ready
        break
      end
    end
  end

  Provider -> DB: CreateSessionEndpoint(\n  conversationID, vmInstanceID,\n  "cc-remote-agent", port)
  DB --> Provider: {id, vmInstanceID, port}
  Provider -> DB: IncrementVMActiveContainers(vmInstanceID)
end

note over Provider: agentURL = http://{internalIP}:{port}
Provider -> Container: remoteclient.NewClient(agentURL).Execute(req, onEvent)
Container -> Container: claude CLI 実行 (ndjson streaming)
Container --> Provider: ndjson stream → onEvent(...)

Provider -> DB: UpdateSessionEndpointLastActivity(conversationID)
Provider --> CloudRun: sessionID

CloudRun -> DB: UPDATE message (content_blocks, status: "done")
CloudRun --> Browser: 202 Accepted

@enduml
